                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Williams</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Adee</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-09-06">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 6, 1896</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Aguirre just released and Sanguily’s case will be tried soon.</p>
